title: Ep 2223 - Varun Unveils New Look Of SAB TV
shortDesc: The members of Gokuldham society get excited to see Varun Dhawan on a big screen. Varun Dhawan unveils the new look of SAB TV in front of Jethalal and his neighbours.

title: Ep 2224 - Popatlal Gets Call From Marriage Bureau
shortDesc: Popatlal gets a call from a marriage bureau. He learns that a girl is interested in meeting him. He excitedly tells Taarak that he would soon get married.

title: Ep 2226 - Jhilmil Meets Popatlal
shortDesc: Jhilmil and her family come to Popatlal’s house to meet him. Popatlal introduces Jhilmil to his neighbours. Jhilmil gets shocked to learn that Popatlal has turned down a chance to interview actor Salman Khan.

title: Ep 2227 - Popatlal Plans To Meet Salman Khan
shortDesc: Jhilmil tells Popatlal that she wants to take a selfie along with Salman Khan. Popatlal requests his boss to let him take Salman Khan’s interview. Popatlal’s boss replies him that the interview is already taken by another reporter.

title: Ep 2228 - Salman Khan Agrees To Meet Popatlal And Friends
shortDesc: A film producer tells Popatlal that Salman Khan is too busy to meet him. Tapu calls Salman Khan and tells him that his friends wishes to meet him. Salman Khan asks them to meet him within an hour.

title: Ep 2230 - Salman Khan Avoids Popatlal
shortDesc: Popatlal tells Salman Khan that his friend wants to take selfie with him. Salman replies Popatlal that he doesn’t want to talk to him. He asks Popatlal as to why he refused to interview him.

title: Ep 2232 - Selfie with Salman Khan
shortDesc: Jhilmil had asked Popatlal for a selfie with Salman. Popatlal tells Salman that Jhilmil can only marry to him if she gets a selfie with Salman. Salman then takes many selfies with everyone from Gokuldham.

title: Ep 2233 - Poppatlals Dream Remains Unfulfilled
shortDesc: The ladies of the Gokuldham society wholeheartedly welcome Jhilmil to their community. But, Jhilmil appears distressed, much to the surprise of the society members.

title: Ep 2234 - Eternal Optimism Of Poppatlal
shortDesc: Poppatlal is left heartbroken after Jhilmil leaves for Ghaziabad, however, he cheers up the members of the Gokuldham society saying that he still retains hope that someday he will get married. Daya arrives at Poppatlal's house to console him.

title: Ep 2235 - Tappu Wants to Visit Goa
shortDesc: Jethalal is worried about Tappu and suspects that he is trying to hide something from him. He is unaware that Tappu is planning is trip with his friends.

title: Ep 2236 - Bhide Too Wants to Visit Goa
shortDesc: Sonu and Madhavi manage to convince Bhide. Now, Sonu, Bhide and Madhavi are also coming on the trip to Goa. After having got their parents consent, Tappu Sena rejoices. But, Roshan Sodhi refuses to give permission to Gogi.

title: Ep 2237 - Bhides Goa Dilemma
shortDesc: The Gokuldham society members are eager to go to Goa. Bhide holds a meeting to plan the trip. During the meeting, Jethalal and Bhide get into an argument. Champaklal, who is enraged with the argument, refuses to come to Goa.
